1.title: Sheklia & Talli
1.plot: A concerned son reaches out when his mom's mysterious online boyfriend seems too shady for comfort. But Mom is hiding secrets of her own, and once Nev & Max find their man, things take a bizarre turn that leave them shocked.

2.title: Alyssa & Tyler
2.plot: When a woman's friend urges her to sign up for a dating website, Nev and Max become suspicious of the "love of her life."

3.title: Kim & Matt
3.plot: After five years of talking to Matt, Kim is ready to meet up with her online love. As Max and Nev try to bring the two together, they uncover buried secrets that threaten to drive a wedge between the two lovers.

4.title: Lawrence & Cierra
4.plot: After a number of near-death experiences, Lawrence survived through it all with the assurance of Cierra's online love. But with Cierra blowing Lawrence off whenever they try to meet, Nev and Max must find the truth behind the suspicious profile.

5.title: Mary & Adam
5.plot: A former catfish turns to Nev and Max for help when they fall hard in love online. This catfish might be playing Nev and Max, or may end up paying for their crimes with a broken heart.

6.title: Zak & Garrett
6.plot: When Zak met Garrett online he fell hard, but suspicious video calls and curious disappearances has Zak worried about who he really fell in love with. Will Nev and Max be able to find Garrett before he vanishes for good?

7.title: Traves & Candy
7.plot: When Traves asks for help with his internet girlfriend Candy, it looks like a classic case of catfishing. But after more pieces of the puzzle come together, the guys realize they may have caught a bigger catfish than expected.

8.title: Mandy & Jose
8.plot: Mandy is in love with a guy that gives her everything except the truth. Mandy's son has had enough and calls in Nev and Max for help. But following a trail of clues only takes them all deeper down the rabbit hole.

9.title: Infiniti & Dave
9.plot: Nev and Max head to New York City to help Infinti, a 19-year-old dancer who is certain that her online romance is the real deal. But when Nev and Max dive deep, they find Infiniti's love interest is far shadier than they ever imagined.

10.title: Dylan & Savenia
10.plot: Dylan's desperately fallen for a beautiful model with an elusive secret. With all the standard red flags, Nev and Max assume it's an open and shut case - but the truth is something stranger than fiction.

11.title: Kiaira & Cortney
11.plot: Kiaira and Cortney had a baby, but the two have never met. Nev and Max are called in to bring the family together, but they worry this could be the greatest manipulation in catfish history.

12.title: Nina & Jon
12.plot: Nina is a sexy webcam model, who's considering leaving her husband for a big spender client she's fallen in love with online. Nev and Max investigate this high stakes case to determine if his big tips come with bigger lies.

13.title: Angel & Jordan
13.plot: A match on Tinder ignited a fire for Jordan that caused Angel to end a real-life relationship to pursue him. When Nev and his wife Laura get on the case they uncover dark truths that could lose Angel everyone close in her life.

14.title: Breana & Josh
14.plot: Breana waits to marry Josh for 11 years, but her love fades when the boys uncover the man behind the profile. Josh's past catches up with him as Nev and Max launch a multistate manhunt to uncover the dark truth.

15.title: Chelsea & Charles
15.plot: Nev and Max agree to help Chelsea finally meet her online boyfriend, Charles, in person; while Chelsea has only spoken to Charles once, on the phone, the guys soon show her that a picture speaks a thousand words.

16.title: Nae & Brandon
16.plot: Nev and Max attempt to help a young woman named Nae track down her elusive internet celebrity crush and soon find themselves embroiled in a catfish conspiracy.

17.title: Derek & Annabelle
17.plot: A mystery email leads Nev and Laura to help Derek track down his online love Annabelle. After digging, they uncover a sexy Snapchat scandal, betrayal, and a conclusion that hits closer to home than Derek could have ever dreamed.

18.title: Nick & Jasmine
18.plot: Nev and Max try to help Nick determine if the person he kissed during a mysterious blindfolded rendezvous is actually his online love, Jasmine, or someone entirely different altogether.

19.title: Mike & Joey
19.plot: Nev and co-host Jane Carrey help aspiring sugar baby Mike choose between his Los Angeles life of leisure and his deep affection for the mysterious Joey, a broke mechanic he fell in love with on Grindr.

20.title: Rachael & Vance
20.plot: Nev and co-host Kamie Crawford fly to Iowa to help Rachael meet Vance, her decade long Myspace romance. As they dig into Vance's past, Rachael is left wondering if he really is the man she spent half her life in love with.

21.title: Sheila & Rich Dollaz
21.plot: Nev and co-host Nick Young, aka Swaggy P, are hot on a case to help Sheila figure out if she's being romanced by "Love and Hip Hop" star Rich Dollaz.

22.title: Chelsea & Lennie
22.plot: Nev and co-host Tallulah Willis help Chelsea, a young woman who's fallen for a reality TV star. Digging for the truth only reveals Chelsea has her own secrets.

23.title: Truth & Ray'Quan
23.plot: Nev and guest co-host Zeke Thomas set out to help fashion design student Truth find out if his online crush Ray'Quan is the real deal.

24.title: Shakinah & Chris
24.plot: After chatting for years with Chris, Shakinah needs to move forward with her love life, but when Nev and co-host Kamie Crawford find out that Chris is a huge pop star, they know Shakinah needs their help in more ways than one.

25.title: Dallas & Safari
25.plot: Model Dallas has had his sights set on sexy Safari ever since she slid into his DMs, but despite flirty promises, she won't meet. Nev and co-host Tallulah Willis take Dallas on a wild ride as they hunt for Safari.

26.title: Aubri & Brian
26.plot: Nev and co-host Slick Woods help 19-year-old Aubri search for her Snapchat love, Brian. Brian says he lives at Aubri's college but makes several excuses not to meet. With little to go on, Nev and Slick hit the campus in search of answers.

27.title: Nique & Alice
27.plot: Co-host popstar, Elle King joins Nev to help Nique find her Tumblr love, Alice. Digging deep leads to more questions than answers as Nev and Elle have concerns about who Alice could be and what her true intentions are with Nique.

28.title: Deven & James
28.plot: Nev and NFL star Rashad Jennings help Deven find his mysterious online love, James. James won't videochat yet he invites Deven to fly across the country to meet him. Hopeful for love but prepared for a trap, Deven needs answers.

1.title: Sunny & Jamison
1.plot: Meet Nev and Max from MTV's newest reality series, Catfish: The TV Show - and find out just who (or what) is a Catfish.

2.title: Trina & Scorpio
2.plot: Trina is an exotic dancer who always had trouble meeting guys she could trust, until she met Scorpio, a fellow dancer, online. Will Trina finally get to rendezvous with the only man she's ever loved?

3.title: Kim & Matt
3.plot: Kim's been pouring her heart out to Matt for over 10 yrs. However, he's refused to get together with her. Now, Kim's facing a life-changing decision -- should she marry her current boyfriend or find out if Matt is her soul mate?

4.title: Jasmine & Mike
4.plot: Jasmine has been texting with Mike for two years and thinks he could be the perfect step-father for her son. Although they live only 15 minutes apart, Jasmine and Mike have yet to meet up in person.

5.title: Jarrod & Abby
5.plot: Jarrod never thought he'd find love--until he fell for Abby on Facebook. Jarrod thinks Abby could be "the one," but she's refusing to see him. What is Abby hiding?

6.title: Kya and Alyx
6.plot: After Kya fell in love online with Alyx, she confessed that she had been using a fake name and pictures when communicating with him. Alyx forgave her immediately and accepted Kya without hesitation. The two have never met.

7.title: Joe & Kari Ann
7.plot: Joe was skeptical when former Miss Teen USA, Kari Ann Peniche, sent him a friend request. Now, after months of intense communication, Joe thinks it might be the real Kari Ann, and that he also might have found love with her.

8.title: Tyler & Amanda
8.plot: Tyler seems to have it all--which is why his friends were so surprised when he fell for Amanda online. After a year and a half of chatting and texting, Tyler thinks they could have a future together.

9.title: Rod & Ebony
9.plot: When Rod met Ebony on a dating web site four years ago, he thought he was talking to a heterosexual woman. But after the two fell in love, Ebony revealed that she is transgender.

10.title: Rico & Ja'mari
10.plot: Rico wants to move to England to care for his ailing mother, but his intense online relationship with Ja'mari, an international male model, is giving him second thoughts about leaving.

11.title: Mike & Felicia
11.plot: When Mike met Felicia through an online dating site, he immediately felt sparks. After a few weeks of constant phone calls and web chats they made plans to meet in person, but Felicia stood him up, making him wonder if he can trust her.

12.title: The Reunion
12.plot: Participants from the second season of 'Catfish: The TV Show' reunite in MTV's Times Square studio to answer questions from fans, 'Catfish' investigators Nev and Max, and host SuChin Pak

0.title: Hooked on Catfish: The Road to Season 2
0.plot: Hosts Nev Schulman and Max Joseph take a break from tracking down wily catfish to unveil a fast-paced, 30-minute preview that highlights the stories of online romance in Catfish Season 2.

1.title: Cassie & Steve
1.plot: Nev and Max have traveled across the country bringing couples together. Check out a few of their pit stops along the way.

2.title: Anthony & Marq
2.plot: Anthony is a Iraq War veteran who wears his Purple Heart on his sleeve. Over a year ago, he bonded online with a caring, emotionally available man named Marq. Today, they're head over heels in love - but what is Marq hiding?

3.title: Ramon & Paola
3.plot: Ramon's one shining glimmer of happiness is Paola, a girl he met on Facebook and established an exclusive online relationship with. But after many failed attempts to video chat with Paola, is she really who he thinks she is?

4.title: Lauren & Derek
4.plot: Lauren met Derek on MySpace nearly 8 years ago! Since then she's relied on him for everything and knows that Derek is the man of her dreams. The only problem is, they've never met in real life or even video chatted.

5.title: Dorion & Jeszica
5.plot: Dorion is torn between two women - his current girlfriend, Raffinee, and his online love of over two years, Jeszica. He's willing to give up everything for Jeszica, including his relationship. But is Jeszica really the girl in the pictures?

6.title: Jen & Skylar
6.plot: After being bullied in her past, Jen relies on online communities to establish relationships. After meeting Skylar online, Jen and Skylar immediately hit it off. But they've never met in person. Will consent to a visit from Jen?

7.title: Mike & Kristen
7.plot: Years ago, Mike met Kristen on Facebook. They quickly forged a deep connection, but Mike's frequent efforts to meet Kristen have been futile. He's convinced she could be the one. Will Mike finally get face-to-face with Kristen?

8.title: Jesse & Brian
8.plot: When Jesse met Brian on Facebook, she thought she'd hit the jackpot. They made plans to meet, but Brian stood her up. Now, years later, Brian has asked her to live with him. But, she can't stop wondering - what is Brian hiding?

9.title: Artis & Jess
9.plot: 5 months ago, Artis met Jess, a blonde beauty, online. Artis and Jess each were in relationships, but believed they'd found true love. Artis is finally ready to meet Jess in person. But is Jess everything that she says she is?

10.title: Ashley & Mike
10.plot: For over seven years, Ashley has sent dramatically altered photos of herself to her soul mate, Mike, to make her look thinner and more attractive to him.

11.title: Aaliyah & Alicia
11.plot: Alicia refuses to meet Aaliyah because she has not come out to her friends and family.

12.title: Aaliyah & Alicia
12.plot: Aaliyah has been able to share her life struggles from with her first girlfriend Alicia. However, despite living only 70 blocks away, Alicia refuses to meet Aaliyah since she hasn't come out to her friends and family yet.

13.title: Nick and Melissa
13.plot: Some first loves are unforgettable. This is the case for Nick, an 18 year-old Florida native who fell in love with Melissa after he met her in an online chat room when he was 12 years old. Now, only months before Nick is set to leave for college and begin a new life, he's determined to visit the girl he calls "his one true love" and find out if she really is the person he's been hanging his hopes on for all these years. Is Melissa the real deal or has Nick been entangled in a web of online lies?

14.title: Keyonnah & Bow Wow
14.plot: Superfan Keyonnah is almost certain that she's been having an online relationship with her childhood crush, the rapper Bow Wow. Now, Keyonnah wants to find out whether her dreams have become reality - or if this relationship is too good to be true.

16.plot: Mike fell in love online with Caroline over a year and a half ago but she has continually evaded his attempts to meet. Strangely though, she often makes her presence known by sending Mike pictures of his workplace and has even left a note on his car.

18.title: Derek & Kristen
18.plot: After some bad luck with girls, Derek meets Kristen on Facebook. After developing a deep love for each other, Derek's ready to meet her. But Kristen always has an excuse. Is Kristen his dream girl, or is Derek out of luck again?

1.title: Craig & Zoe
1.plot: Craig met Zoe on Facebook and quickly developed a deep relationship with her. But things turned sour when Zoe began demanding passwords and hacking his accounts. Craig is determined to find out who he really gave his heart to.

2.title: Antwane & Tony
2.plot: Carmen is concerned about her cousin Antwane's 3-year romance with a man named Tony. Antwane lives a virtually pre-digital age existence making Tony's true identity difficult to reveal. Is Tony really who he says he is?

3.title: Antoinette & Albert
3.plot: A year after meeting "T-lights" on Instagram, "instaceleb" Antointette is ready to take things to the next level and meet "T-lights", but he always brushes off the idea. Is "T-lights" really the online celebrity he claims to be?

4.title: Lucille & Kidd Cole
4.plot: Lucille led a simple life until she was asked to work for an up and coming music producer named Kidd Cole. Companies were never paid for their services and one day Kidd couldn't be found. Will Lucille get the answers she needs?

5.title: Tracie & Sammie
5.plot: Actress Tracie Thoms develops an emotional connection with a fan named Sammie.

6.title: John & Kelsey
6.plot: John is ready to leave Detroit but one thing holds him back: Kelsey. The two have never spoken outside of online chats but John is sure she's the one. With such a big life change in front of John, can he include Kelsey in plans?

7.title: Solana & Elijah
7.plot: Solana wants to take her relationship with her boyfriend Danny to the next level but she can't stop thinking about her online love Elijah. His photos were used in so many profiles that Solana has to know is this the real Elijah?

8.title: Miranda & Cameryn
8.plot: After years of online chats and late night calls Miranda discovered that Cameryn was not the man he claimed to be. She confronted him only to be given another suspicious profile. Is the man she loves someone else entirely?

9.title: Jeff & Megan
9.plot: Jeff believes Megan is the perfect girl for him. After talking for over a year, Jeff is ready to take big steps, possibly leaving his military career and home behind, just to find out once and for all, if Megan is his dream girl.

12.title: Bianca & Brogan
12.plot: When broken disappears from the internet, then returns online after a year without question, Bianca wants to know what happened in the missing year.

13.title: Special
13.plot: This hour-long special will give viewers a dynamic way to relive weird but true catfishing tales. Featuring Nev and Max as hosts, the specials will include interviews with the real-life participants sharing their wild, crazy, and bizarre experiences.

14.title: Special: Part 2
14.plot: This special episode features some wild catfish tales as told by the people who experienced the real events, reenactments by actors and commentary from Nev and Max.

0.title: The Untold Stories Part 3
0.plot: Nev and Max tell more crazy-Catfish stories.

1.title: Miracle and Javonni
1.plot: Single mom Miracle falls for Javonni, a dreamy-eyed Instagram user.

2.title: Courtney and Isaak
2.plot: After a girl cuts ties with an Internet beau, he refuses to give up trying to get her back.

3.title: Harold & Armani
3.plot: A guy finds his match in the same neighborhood, but never meets her.

4.title: Daisy and Marcus
4.plot: After helping with troubles at home, a man refuses to speak to his love interest on the phone.

5.title: Chitara & Priscilla
5.plot: A woman searches for answers when her relationship ends unexpectedly.

6.title: Felipe & Jasmine
6.plot: A single father wants to settle down with his online love, but they have not met.

7.title: Stephanie & David
7.plot: After Stephanie's parents' divorce, she began to question whether she could ever trust a man in a relationship. But then she met David online and immediately developed a deep bond with him.

8.title: Whitney & Bre
8.plot: After meeting on an LGBT site four years ago, a couple has yet to even engage in a video chat.

9.title: Jamey and Ari
9.plot: After falling for a fellow Texan online, a man will do anything to meet his love.

10.title: Blaire & Markie
10.plot: Even though a young woman faced heartache from an instagram lover, she is still eager to meet.

11.title: Steven & Samm
11.plot: Rather than plan for college, a young man wants to move to California to support his online love.

12.title: Where Are They Now?
12.plot: Max hits the road to catch up with some of his favorite hopefuls and catfish from the first two seasons. Have the hopefuls found true love? Are the catfish still catfishing? Max won't come home until he's gotten the answers.

13.title: Tiana & James
13.plot: A young woman moves across the country to be with her Internet love, but he is being elusive.

14.title: Falesha & Jacqueline
14.plot: After her name and pictures were stolen, nearly ruining her life, a young woman is haunted.

15.title: Prophet & Trinity
15.plot: While launching his comeback, a rapper connects with someone online, and now is ready to settle down.

16.title: Thad & Sara
16.plot: Thaddius sought refuge from his struggling marriage through an online relationship with Sara. But, when Sara starts telling strange tales of seizures and kidnappings, Thaddius starts to question her true identity.

17.title: Andria & David
17.plot: David is the only love Andria has ever known. His passionate love letters and voice messages have a way of making Andria stay. But having never met after 10 years, Andria needs to know what David is hiding that keeps him away.

18.title: Hundra & Emily
18.plot: Hundra never planned on falling in love with a girl and now she is risking coming out on national TV to learn if her love with Emily is for real. Special guest Machine Gun Kelly teams with Nev to reveal a shocking Catfish.

19.title: Devan & Rylan
19.plot: For shy Devan, meeting Rylan was love at first click. Devan wants to believe that Rylan is marriage material but, her suspicious behavior is leaving him with doubts. Special guest Todrick Hall helps Nev uncover the truth.

20.title: Brittany & Bryon
20.plot: When Brittany, a single mom, finds love online with Bryon, a marine who may get deployed again to Iraq, she seeks Nev and Max's help before she runs out of time to discover if her seemingly perfect military man is real.

1.title: Dejay, Malik & Josiah
1.plot: Nev and Max get two catfishes for the price of one when they discover that Dejay and Malik are being played by the same guy. Sparks fly as they discover just how explosive a love triangle can be.

2.title: Jeanette & Derick
2.plot: Mama doesn't always know best. Concerned daughter, Shuntay, enlists the help of Nev and Max after her mother, Jeanette, begins talking about marriage and uprooting her family to be with a man who refuses to meet in person.

3.title: Leuh & Justin
3.plot: Since Leuh saw surfer Justin it's been insta-love ever since. But after 2 failed attempts to meet up, she's desperate to figure out if Justin really is the man of her dreams or is she one in a long line of online lovers.

4.title: Brandon & McKenna
4.plot: Brandon loves McKenna, but failed attempts to connect has left him wondering if McKenna is for real. Nev teams with social media sensation Karrueche Tran to help Brandon uncover the shocking truth of his true love.

5.title: Jaylin & Ja'la
5.plot: Jaylin is prepared to sacrifice a lifelong friendship and promising videogame career to be with a woman he's never even spoken to on the phone. Nev and Max help him discover that sometimes the truth is stranger than fiction.

6.title: Michael & Chanelle
6.plot: Michael's brother emailed Nev and Max as he does not think Chanelle is who she says she is. A DM from Chanelle to Michael, starts their friendship but then, Chanelle disappears...

7.title: Ray & Lexi
7.plot: Ray is determined to finally meet his online love of four years, Lexi. But after learning that Lexi's sister has meddled in the relationship in the past, Nev and Max soon find themselves with more questions than answers.

8.title: Joanna & Bo
8.plot: Tattoo model, Joanna, was about to meet her online love in the flesh, but a crazy night in Vegas caused the whole relationship to go sour. Now she's enlisted Nev and Max to help track down her former flame and make things right.

9.title: Tyreme & Tomorrow
9.plot: In this special episode of Catfish, Nev and Max reunite past Catfish and their victims who parted on bad terms to follow up on what life has been like since the show and to help them find a better resolution.

10.title: Kayla & Courtney
10.plot: A woman receives a message from someone claiming to be channeling the spirit of her father, who committed suicide after murdering her mother.

11.title: Paris & Tara
11.plot: Paris enlists Nev and Max to help her figure out who has been catfishing her for the past four years. But as the guys investigate, they make a shocking discovery that casts suspicion onto Paris herself!

12.title: Vince & Alyssa
12.plot: A man cannot escape his online ex, whose stalking has caused his real girlfriend to break up with him.

13.title: Lucas & Many
13.plot: Former Playboy model, Jayme, has learned that her online boyfriend is not only fake, but appears to be catfishing other women as well! She enlists Nev and Max to help find the catfish and put an end to his perverted deception.

14.title: Larissa & Anthony
14.plot: Larissa meets Anthony. Larissa is naive and has been catfished before, but will she be catfished again by Anthony?

15.title: Spencer & Katy
15.plot: Spencer reveals that he has been having a relationship with a pop star, and the Catfish team sets out to find the truth.

16.title: Candic & Titus
16.plot: After months of intimate text exchanges with a man she met online, named Titus, Candic has decided to finally stop and fess up to her husband. But before she does, she needs Nev and Max to help her find out who Titus really is!

17.title: Andrea, Alex & Andrea
17.plot: Nev and Max are summoned to help catch a potential stalker who is impersonating the family of a popular online personality.

18.title: Catherine & Graham
18.plot: A woman from Long Island, N.Y, prepares to relocate to Tennessee for her internet love.

19.title: Luis & Sydney
19.plot: After falling for a single mother, a man wants to take their online relationship to the next level.

20.title: Andrew & Zach
20.plot: Andrew thought he met the perfect match on Tinder in Zac until he received a text message from a friend revealing shocking new information. As Nev and Max look into the case, they suspect Zac could be keeping a very big secret.

1.title: Shawny & Jack
1.plot: A newly single woman wants help uncovering the identity of her new love, but she may have secrets of her own.

2.title: Alante & Nevaeh
2.plot: Alante has spent the last 8 years planning a life with his online love Nevaeh. She's perfect but her disappearances have Alante worried. Nev and Max help to uncover a mysterious truth that affects Alante's entire town.

3.title: Danny & Rosa
3.plot: Danny is intent on building a family with his beautiful online love, despite her violent past. But when he enlists Nev and Max to help him finally meet her in person, they soon discover she may have ties to a former Catfish!

4.title: Telizza & Shai
4.plot: 18-year-old Telizza became bi-curious when her online friendship with Shai turned romantic. Frustrated by several failed attempts to video chat, Telizza has turned to Nev and Max to uncover the truth.

5.title: Marvin & Austin
5.plot: After months of sexting with a hot model he met on a hookup app, Marvin is eager to meet him in person. Max and sidekick, singer Chantal Claret, agree to help Marvin find his crush, but soon uncover more than they bargained for!

6.title: Mecca & Tanner
6.plot: Max and co-host iO Tillett Wright help 18-year-old Mecca connect with the boy she's loved for the past 5 years. But when iO discovers that Mecca's digital beau may be using her pictures to catfish others, Mecca needs answers.

7.title: Yasmine & Lewis
7.plot: When Sandra learns that her granddaughter, Yasmine, sent money to a mysterious online boyfriend, she asks Nev and Max for help. As the guys look into the case, they discover there's much more that Yasmine has been hiding.

8.title: Kailani & Sam
8.plot: Kailani has fallen for Sam, her gay friend's online ex-boyfriend. Sam claims to love Kailani, but has been dodgy since she has tried to meet up with him. Nev and Max investigate Sam to help Kailani uncover what he is hiding.

9.title: Ari & Lanum
9.plot: Nev and Max receive emails from opposite sides of the same online romance, each concerned that the other may be a catfish. The guys are taken aback when one side decides to follow through with their marriage plans.

10.title: Dylan & Ally
10.plot: Dylan receives an anonymous text warning him that his online love, Ally, is not who she says she is, and enlists Nev and Max to help find her. After the mystery texter is revealed, the guys uncover a huge web of deceit.

11.title: Colleen & Tony
11.plot: Colleen met Tony online and fell madly in love. Though they've never met, Tony proposed to Colleen over the phone and she accepted. Now, Nev and Max help her finally face the truth to reveal the mystery man she's engaged to.

12.title: Open Investigation
12.plot: Nev and Max embark on the biggest case of their lives as they track down the infamous, Shelly Chartier, to uncover new truths as they investigate the celebrity catfishing of Paris Roxanne and NBA star, Chris "Birdman" Andersen.

13.title: Johnny & Connor
13.plot: After Jonathon's online love disappears for a month, he enlists Nev and Max to help track him down. But when the guys discover a former catfish is involved, they begin to suspect Jonathon himself may be in on the deception.

14.title: Kelsie & Brandon
14.plot: Southern sweetheart Kelsie is madly in love with her online romeo, Brandon. But after years of endless excuses of why he cannot meet up, Kelsie recruits Nev and Max to go deep in the heart of Texas to find who Brandon really is.

15.title: April & Dean
15.plot: It's been seven years since April met Dean in a chat room at the age of thirteen. During that time, Dean would often disappear for months at a time. Now, Nev and Max must help April find Dean before he disappears again.

16.title: Robert & Ashleigh
16.plot: After being paralyzed as a teenager, Robert met Ashleigh online and they fell in love. With news he may not have much longer to live, Robert asks Nev and Max to bring Ashleigh to him so he can find out if their love was real.

17.title: Robin & Wayne
17.plot: After three long years, Robin is desperate to finally meet her elusive, hunky, long-distance love in person. Nev and Max agree to help her hunt him down, but what they uncover turns out to be much more than Robin bargained for.

18.title: Nicole & Nicole
18.plot: For years, Nicole has had her pictures stolen to make fake profiles, one of which has been catfishing lovelorn, 27-year-old Ryan for 10 years. Is this a random internet troll or do Ryan and Nicole have a common enemy?

19.title: Jose & Jay
19.plot: Jasmine writes to Nev and Max asking for help for a "friend." But they're perplexed when Jasmine drops a bombshell revelation: they've helped her friend before. Who is Jasmine's mysterious friend and how do Nev and Max know him?

20.title: Caitlyn & Kenton
20.plot: Young mother Caitlyn calls on Nev and Max to help separate the fact from fiction of her courtship with charming Facebook hunk, Kenton. Kenton insists she and her daughter move to Kentucky but is Kenton all that he claims to be?

1.plot: Feel the thrill of the hunt as hosts Nev and Charlamagne tha God relive the most exciting pursuits, craziest investigative tricks, and greatest lengths Nev and Max have gone toâ€¦TO CATCH A CATFISH!

imdb.plot outline: Tackles the mystery and complexities of dating in a digital world. According to an MTV survey of Millenials 18-24 years old, 1 in 4 has online dated, 1 in 2 has a friend who does it and, in the past three years, traffic to top 10 online dating sites has tripled. In a world where everyone is constantly connected digitally, social media has made communicating easier but this digital world might also complicate relationships.
imdb.title: Catfish: The TV Show
plot: 'Nev Schulman' (qv) and 'Max Joseph' (qv) help people who have fallen in love online test the authenticity of their lovers' identities.

Tackles the mystery and complexities of dating in a digital world. According to an MTV survey of Millenials 18-24 years old, 1 in 4 has online dated, 1 in 2 has a friend who does it and, in the past three years, traffic to top 10 online dating sites has tripled. In a world where everyone is constantly connected digitally, social media has made communicating easier but this digital world might also complicate relationships.::Anonymous
